-- Tata Hires Morgan Stanley for Cable & Wireless Bid, Times Says
-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 2012-03-25T07:09:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-25/tata-hires-morgan-stanley-for-cable-wireless-bid-times-says.html
Tata Communications Ltd. (TCOM)  hired
 Morgan Stanley (MS)  as it considers a bid for  Cable & Wireless
Worldwide Plc (CW/) , the Sunday Times reported, without saying how it
obtained the information.  Standard Chartered (STAN)  is already advising Mumbai-based Tata
Communications on the potential purchase, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
 m.carr@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
